::Kluster/Shredder::

Kluster jerks his head up as he hears Whistler's yell, tearing his 
eyes off the scan reports and other data he had been going over. 
Megatron, KitKat, Arachnia, all together... This could not be good for 
the Maximals.

"Come on in," he yells down the corridor, turning his head back to 
review the reports. Behind him, Shredder frowns. This was taking a bit 
too long for his taste.
